News.Title: Dhanlaxmi Crop Science: Shares Soar 90% on NSE SME Debut
News.Summary: Dhanlaxmi Crop Science shares listed at ₹104.5 on NSE SME, a 90% premium over the IPO price of ₹55. The IPO, which raised ₹23.80 crore, was oversubscribed 555.83 times. The company specializes in technology-driven seed development for crops and vegetables.
